    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Buildings, sites, districts, structures, or objects that possess national cultural significance, according to criteria established by the National Park Service of the United States.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
